00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:12,119
I can't help but feel bad for them.

288
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,519
Do as you please, then.

289
00:30:25,519 --> 00:30:27,160
So which is the best way up?

290
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,680
What are these ropes?

291
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:47,640
Please help.

292
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:51,039
What's wrong wit him?

293
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,160
He vomits out everything he ate.

294
00:33:53,279 --> 00:33:54,880
Been flat on his back for days.

295
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,079
If it's not sacrilege, it's just karma.

296
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:59,079
If it's not sacrilege, it's just karma.

297
00:34:00,519 --> 00:34:03,680
The Great Mother will take this burden.

298
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,800
What are you doing?

299
00:34:44,159 --> 00:34:44,800
Hey! Enough!

300
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,320
Enough.

301
00:34:48,039 --> 00:34:48,599
Who are you?

302
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:49,400
Leave.

303
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:50,920
How did thou get here?

304
00:34:54,079 --> 00:34:55,000
What are you trying to do?

305
00:34:55,559 --> 00:34:56,800
Are you trying to kill her?

306
00:34:57,679 --> 00:34:58,719
Who art thou?

307
00:34:59,239 --> 00:35:01,519
Why are thou ruining our sacred ritual?

308
00:35:02,239 --> 00:35:05,679
The Great Mother atones for our sins.

309
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,280
Get out.

310
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,800
The Great Mother?

311
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:11,760
A statue

312
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,360
atoning for people?

313
00:35:14,519 --> 00:35:15,960
Then why don't you whip the statue?

314
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,360
Why are you hurting her?

315
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,000
This isn't a ritual.

316
00:35:22,119 --> 00:35:23,119
It's murder.

317
00:35:23,920 --> 00:35:27,119
The Spirit Medium is the Great Mother's vessel.

318
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,519
How could you let them do this to you?

319
00:35:33,159 --> 00:35:34,480
No human or god

320
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,039
can atone for others' sin.

321
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,599
You are not a vessel.

322
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:39,840
You are a human.

323
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:44,000
Who falls prey to these sickening minds.

324
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:50,039
She has rights in her own life and body.

325
00:35:51,199 --> 00:35:52,960
What rights do you have treating her this way?

326
00:35:54,519 --> 00:35:55,639
The Great Mother?

327
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,480
Don't hide in her name.

328
00:35:59,639 --> 00:36:00,840
Stop using your faith

329
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:02,599
and your agenda

330
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,119
to cause scars on innocent people.

331
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,719
Leave this village now!

332
00:36:14,199 --> 00:36:14,880
What are you doing?

333
00:36:28,559 --> 00:36:30,480
Take him out!

334
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:32,679
Let go!

335
00:36:34,639 --> 00:36:35,920
This isn't right!

336
00:36:36,199 --> 00:36:37,840
Do not let him set foot in our village again.

337
00:36:38,119 --> 00:36:39,719
A man’s duty is to protect a woman!

338
00:36:40,079 --> 00:36:41,239
Not hurting her like this.

339
00:36:42,239 --> 00:36:43,159
Let go!

340
00:36:47,119 --> 00:36:47,840
Let go!

341
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,239
Leave!

342
00:36:49,719 --> 00:36:51,239
Don't let them do this to you.

343
00:36:52,119 --> 00:36:53,480
You are a human, not god.

344
00:36:54,119 --> 00:36:55,119
Get out!

345
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,480
Get out!

346
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:13,840
Leave.

347
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:15,960
And don't you ever come back.

348
00:37:20,039 --> 00:37:22,599
So this is why you want the isolation?

349
00:37:23,679 --> 00:37:26,559
To hide all these fucked-ups from the outside world?

350
00:37:31,119 --> 00:37:32,639
If you come back here,

351
00:37:34,079 --> 00:37:35,280
thou shall be dead.

352
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,199
A statue

353
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:29,800
atoning for people?

354
00:38:30,519 --> 00:38:32,280
Then why don't you whip

355
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,800
the statue?

356
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:37,519
How could you let them do this to you?

357
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:40,079
You are not a vessel.

358
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,079
You are a human.

359
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:46,159
Who falls prey to these sickening minds

360
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:07,199
Brew this.

361
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:10,760
So your wounds will quickly healed.

362
00:39:15,519 --> 00:39:16,480
What's wrong?

363
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,599
Just thinking about that man.

364
00:39:33,079 --> 00:39:35,599
Why is he saying that?

365
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:40,960
Only the Great Mother Suli

366
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,400
stands above us here.

367
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:48,400
And the Spirit Medium is chosen by her.

368
00:39:51,639 --> 00:39:53,199
Don't pay him no mind.

369
00:39:55,199 --> 00:39:59,599
The Spirit Medium is born to fulfill heaven's sacred duty.

370
00:40:01,599 --> 00:40:02,800
The Great Mother

371
00:40:04,119 --> 00:40:06,480
has love and mercy for you more than anyone.

372
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:12,239
You have to repay her

373
00:40:12,559 --> 00:40:15,119
with lifelong allegiance.

374
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:27,960
Grilled sticky rice.

375
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:31,599
I grilled it myself. It's delicious.

376
00:41:32,559 --> 00:41:33,920
Eat up.

377
00:41:39,159 --> 00:41:40,559
Is your daughter alright?

378
00:41:41,679 --> 00:41:42,599
Yes, Elder.

379
00:41:43,239 --> 00:41:45,960
Thanks to the Great Mother taking up on her sins.

380
00:41:46,159 --> 00:41:47,639
So she is alive.

381
00:41:52,599 --> 00:41:53,480
Elder...

382
00:41:53,519 --> 00:41:54,639
Where is the Spirit Medium ?

383
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:58,400
I can't breathe well.

384
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:00,960
Something is burning in my chest.

385
00:42:01,599 --> 00:42:03,920
I want the Great Mother to atone for me.

386
00:42:04,559 --> 00:42:06,280
I saw the Spirit Medium near the creek.

387
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,559
She's probably fetching water.

388
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:10,559
Elder...

389
00:42:11,159 --> 00:42:12,639
Last night, my husband went out to set traps

390
00:42:13,159 --> 00:42:14,599
and saw that man from yesterday.

391
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:18,000
I don't know if he's gonna cause more havocs to our village.

392
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:21,719
Why are thou back here?

393
00:43:23,199 --> 00:43:26,000
Because I want to help you.

394
00:43:27,519 --> 00:43:29,039
Do you really want to be here?

395
00:43:35,199 --> 00:43:37,840
Heaven told me to be the Spirit Medium, so I have to be it.

396
00:43:40,079 --> 00:43:41,760
It's your own life, so why can't you make your own choice?

397
00:43:44,480 --> 00:43:46,199
There's no such thing as a heaven's decree.

398
00:43:47,840 --> 00:43:49,079
You are a victim.

399
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:52,559
Victim to those fanatics.

400
00:43:58,039 --> 00:43:59,119
I still stand by

401
00:44:00,119 --> 00:44:01,199
to what I've told you.

402
00:44:02,559 --> 00:44:03,679
Your life belongs to you.

403
00:44:06,119 --> 00:44:07,280
You are the master of your own life.

404
00:44:25,280 --> 00:44:26,280
Please believe me.

405
00:44:29,480 --> 00:44:30,400
Don't stay here.

406
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:42,000
I can't leave.

407
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:45,800
Why?

408
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:50,880
I was chosen to be the Spirit Medium since I was little.

409
00:44:57,360 --> 00:44:58,440
The chosen one

410
00:45:02,320 --> 00:45:04,679
has to take this duty to death.

411
00:45:08,039 --> 00:45:08,960
You can leave.

412
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,519
Those fucked up rules

413
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:15,719
were made up just to keep you here.

414
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:20,079
What happened to you

415
00:45:21,760 --> 00:45:22,639
are not right.

416
00:45:25,039 --> 00:45:26,239
Since you became the Spirit Medium,

417
00:45:27,159 --> 00:45:28,840
have you ever been genuinely happy?

418
00:45:41,320 --> 00:45:43,320
Then why take all that beating?

419
00:45:45,800 --> 00:45:46,920
All those beating

420
00:45:47,199 --> 00:45:48,800
wouldn't cleanse anyone's sin.

421
00:45:59,880 --> 00:46:01,840
You have every right to your own happiness.

422
00:46:11,960 --> 00:46:13,000
Let's leave.

423
00:46:13,559 --> 00:46:14,480
I can't.

424
00:46:20,039 --> 00:46:21,239
If I leave,

425
00:46:24,840 --> 00:46:26,159
the Great Mother will take my life.

426
00:46:31,280 --> 00:46:32,159
The Great Mother?

427
00:46:33,559 --> 00:46:34,599
That statue?

428
00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:37,079
It's just a statue.

429
00:46:38,000 --> 00:46:39,880
Build to keep you in blind faith.

430
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:41,400
It can't kill you.

431
00:46:44,639 --> 00:46:45,639
Trust me,

432
00:46:46,400 --> 00:46:47,840
leave this hell hole.

433
00:46:49,519 --> 00:46:50,920
This isn't your home.

434
00:46:52,320 --> 00:46:53,360
If you want a go,

435
00:46:53,639 --> 00:46:54,880
I'll help you.

436
00:47:00,880 --> 00:47:01,760
Believe me.

437
00:47:04,039 --> 00:47:06,760
There are places in the world where you can be happy.

438
00:47:10,159 --> 00:47:11,119
Please come with me.

439
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:15,360
Why art thou helping me?

440
00:47:17,679 --> 00:47:18,719
I'm a man.

441
00:47:20,440 --> 00:47:22,519
A man’s duty is to protect a woman.

442
00:47:37,480 --> 00:47:38,599
Trust me.

443
00:47:43,440 --> 00:47:44,360
Come with me.

444
00:47:44,920 --> 00:47:45,760
Spirit Medium!

445
00:47:49,400 --> 00:47:50,599
Come back to the village immediately.

446
00:47:57,519 --> 00:47:58,920
If you want to have your own life,

447
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:00,599
don't go back.

448
00:48:02,239 --> 00:48:03,119
Spirit Medium!

449
00:48:04,599 --> 00:48:05,039
Come back!

450
00:48:06,840 --> 00:48:08,719
Don't you dare think of leaving.

451
00:48:09,760 --> 00:48:11,000
The town is hell.

452
00:48:16,960 --> 00:48:18,800
And where is heaven?

453
00:48:24,280 --> 00:48:28,079
This place never felt like a heaven to me.

454
00:48:35,760 --> 00:48:39,280
Can I not be a Spirit Medium anymore?

455
00:48:42,679 --> 00:48:44,639
I don't want to be.

456
00:48:45,519 --> 00:48:46,719
You are blessed with that honor.

457
00:48:47,960 --> 00:48:49,360
Why do you have such vile thoughts?

458
00:48:55,440 --> 00:48:56,880
Take the Spirit Medium back to the village!

459
00:48:57,599 --> 00:48:58,280
Run!

460
00:48:59,800 --> 00:49:00,320
Go!

461
00:49:00,679 --> 00:49:01,440
After them!

462
00:49:12,679 --> 00:49:13,519
Careful.

463
00:49:20,000 --> 00:49:20,880
Cross.

464
00:49:21,480 --> 00:49:22,199
Hurry.

465
00:49:57,679 --> 00:49:59,039
Find Muifei.

466
00:49:59,280 --> 00:50:00,719
Don't let her leave the village.

467
00:50:00,960 --> 00:50:01,800
Spead out.

468
00:50:02,000 --> 00:50:02,840
Go there.

469
00:50:03,199 --> 00:50:04,039
Here, Mui.

470
00:50:05,199 --> 00:50:06,519
She's an illegal, then?

471
00:50:06,880 --> 00:50:08,039
I have to detain her.

472
00:50:08,239 --> 00:50:09,519
She's in trouble.

473
00:50:10,159 --> 00:50:11,920
Let her settle down here for a while, Mom.

474
00:50:12,199 --> 00:50:15,119
You brought an illegal into my shop?

475
00:50:15,239 --> 00:50:17,039
If my shop gets shut down, we’re all fucked!

476
00:50:18,320 --> 00:50:19,159
Why are you arresting me?

477
00:50:19,199 --> 00:50:20,000
I've done nothing wrong!

478
00:50:20,320 --> 00:50:21,119
Get him to the station!

479
00:50:21,719 --> 00:50:22,239
Mui!

480
00:50:22,559 --> 00:50:23,119
Mui!
